##Getting started
Press `Ctrl+e` or `Cmd+e` and start typing!  
Press `Ctrl+s` or `Cmd+s` to save  
Press `Ctrl+m` or `Cmd+m` to create a new post  
Press `Backspace` to go back to archive  

Press `?` to view shortcuts/hotkeys
